
Window Attribute Tags
=====================

Usage: OpenWindowTagList_/Windowtags

WA_Zoom: ( ti_Tag=$8000007D )

Specify a pointer to an array of four 
WORDS in ti_Data to set the LeftEdge,
TopEdge, Width and Height values for the
"zoomed" window. 
This implies that a Zoom gadget is required.


