Window Attribute Tags
=====================

Usage: OpenWindowTagList_/Windowtags

WA_SimpleRefresh: ( ti_Tag=$8000008C )

The application will take full
responsibility for updating the window.

NB. Only specify if True.


Window Attribute Tags
=====================

Usage: OpenWindowTagList_/Windowtags

WA_SmartRefresh: ( ti_Tag=$8000008D )

Intuition handles all window updating except
for parts of the window revealed when the window
is sized larger.

NB. Only specify if True.


